item.dc:creator: @Trxkin Trxkin
item.description:
@Trxkin wrote:

Name: Camrin
Your Experience: 3 years
What Position: Admin or co owner. Sense I’ve been owner of 6 different servers which all had over 450 players + on there at all times.
Why should i let you join: You should let me join, because I’m a good owner/admin. And i will help you get players like i have in the past.
How Will I Reach You: You can reach me on via msn. czar101@hotmail.com
or via skype: trxter101
Do you have a mic: Yes i do. I’ll use it whenever you need me to.
Other Information: I’ve coded for about 4 years. But for the first year i wasn’t that good. Then i got better the next 3 years. I’ll be on almost everyday, unless i have to go see my girlfriend, go to my dads, or go to work. Other than that, i’ll be on.

Thanks for readying this.

If you are interested in making me staff. Please PM me on here. Thanks.
